Ns 1⁄4 NH3Oþ þ NOH þ NH2O; (9b)
Nq 1⁄4 NH3Oþ  NOH þ mðNMþ  NM Þ: (9c)
Note that the net charge is neutralized by counterions that are not explicitly considered in the simplified model.
